descriptionHtml:
FashionGo app is the perfect tool for wholesale retailers on the go looking to purchase the latest wholesale trends from top brands & manufacturers.

- Shop thousands of new styles everyday
View new arrivals by vendors you love. You can also filter for items that are in-stock, on vendor’s special promotions, or exclusive to FashionGo

- Personalize your search with Style Match+
Find exactly what you want and shop your inspirations instantly with Style Match+. Search with an image to find the style and compare.

- Purchase, manage, and track your orders
Take FashionGo wherever you go to continue growing your business. You can purchase, manage and track your orders on the go.  

- Check out multiple carts at one time
Simply check out once for all your orders – doesn’t matter how many vendors.

- Save costs on shipping
Consolidated Shipping helps you save time and costs. Receive one shipment for all your orders.

 Register for free on the FashionGo App today and start shopping for your business!
